front.title: •Focused Attack
front.gametext: If Vader is present during a battle at a site, for remainder of turn, he loses his immunity to attrition, but adds ability to power (he may not apply ability toward drawing battle destiny). OR During a duel, add one destiny to your total.
front.lore: Not since his duel with Obi-Wan had Vader unleashed the raw power of the dark side.
